/* src/components/RecordKeeping.astro */
---

<div class="record-keeping-box not-content">
  <div class="header">
    <h3>Keeping Records</h3>
    <p>
      Before lodging an application, start keeping clear and detailed records
      immediately.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-container">
    <div class="column">
      <div class="col-title">
        <span class="icon">ðŸ“„</span> Expenses to track
      </div>
      <ul class="check-list">
        <li>
          <strong>Medical costs:</strong> GP, dental, and specialist fees.
        </li>
        <li><strong>Counselling:</strong> Psychology or psychiatry costs.</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Travel:</strong> Fuel, parking, or public transport tickets for
          appointments.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Lost income:</strong> Payslips or records of unpaid leave.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Reports:</strong> The cost of obtaining medical evidence.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="column">
      <div class="col-title">
        <span class="icon">ðŸ’¡</span> Best practices
      </div>
      <ul class="tip-list">
        <li>
          <strong>Log it as you go:</strong> Use a simple notebook or phone note to
          record dates and costs immediately.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Take photos:</strong> Receipts fade. Take a photo of every receipt
          and physical injury immediately.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Digital backup:</strong> Email photos to yourself or save them in
          a secure private folder so they aren't lost.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <strong>Why is this important?</strong>
    These documents are essential to your claim and directly affect the amount of
    compensation awarded. You will need to attach copies to your application form.
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .record-keeping-box {
    background-color: white;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .header {
    background-color: #f9fafb;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
  }

  .header h3 {
    color: #78081c;
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .header p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .grid-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .grid-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .column {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .column {
      border-bottom: none;
      border-right: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
    }
    .column:last-child {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }

  .col-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.5;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .check-list li::before {
    content: "âœ“";
    color: #78081c;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .tip-list li::before {
    content: "â€¢";
    color: #78081c;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.2rem;
  }

  .footer {
    background-color: #fff1f2;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #881337;
    border-top: 1px solid #fecdd3;
  }
</style>
